# Etherscan API keys for ETH / USDT / USDC balance scanning.
# Get free keys at https://etherscan.io/myapikey (one key per account, free tier).
# Providing all 3 keys rotates requests across them, tripling effective throughput.
# With 3 keys: each key stays under 5 req/sec → scans 400 wallets in ~55 seconds.
# Without keys: falls back to public Ethereum JSON-RPC (slower, no registration needed).
VITE_ETHERSCAN_KEY_1=your_first_etherscan_key
VITE_ETHERSCAN_KEY_2=your_second_etherscan_key
VITE_ETHERSCAN_KEY_3=your_third_etherscan_key
